  <div>
    <div class="card" style="width: 18rem; height: 200px;">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="..." alt="Card image cap">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h2 class="card-text">Convenient</h2>
        <p class="card-text">Browse cars only that are nearby you. Save time and effort to you can run your errands as soon as you can.</p>
      </div>
